\(r_{p} = \frac{Cov(x, y)}{\sqrt{Var(x)}\sqrt{Var(y)}} = \frac{\sum_i^n(X_i-\overline{X})(Y_i-\overline{Y})}{\sqrt{\sum_i^n(X_i-\overline{X})^2}\sqrt{\sum_i^n(Y_i-\overline{Y})^2}}\)
